description: Returns the status of a ChangeToken that you got by calling GetChangeToken. ChangeTokenStatus is one of the following values:    PROVISIONED: You requested the change token by calling GetChangeToken, but you haven't used it yet in a call to create, update, or delete an AWS WAF object.    PENDING: AWS WAF is propagating the create, update, or delete request to all AWS WAF servers.    IN_SYNC: Propagation is complete.
